data.name: label4.Text
data.value: To make a reservation at Stilo Hotel, you can either call us directly at (02) 8888-2003, 2343-1023 loc. 489, +634 8601 1112, +634 8745 1012 loc. 543 or 249 or visit our website at www.Stilohotels.com the website, you can view all the rooms, then select your desired dates, room type, click on the "Book Now" button, and confirm your booking. If you need help, feel free to reach out through email at reservation@stilohotel.com or drop by in person. We're here to help you get set up!

data.name: label5.Text
data.value: Yes, you can choose your desired room directly on our website! Just visit www.stilohotels.com, go to the “ROOMS" section, and browse through the available room types to pick the one that suits you best.

data.name: label8.Text
data.value: The rooms at Stilo Hotel come with cozy beds, free Wi-Fi, a flat-screen TV, and air conditioning. You'll also find a private bathroom with complimentary toiletries, and fresh towels. It's all about comfort and relaxation!

data.name: label11.Text
data.value: To check in at Stilo Hotel, you'll need a valid ID and your booking confirmation (either a printed copy or a digital one on your phone). If you booked online, just show the reservation details sent to your email. For extra convenience, bring the card you used for the booking in case there’s a need for verification.

data.name: label17.Text
data.value: If the reservation is canceled before seven (7) days from the check-in date, the guest will receive a full refund and no cancellation fees will be charged. but if the reservation is canceled within seven (7) days from the check-in date, the hotel will charge 25% of the total booking reservation.

data.name: label20.Text
data.value: Yes, you can request a refund if your booking qualifies under our cancellation policy. If you cancel within the allowed time, you’ll get a full refund. If you cancel after that, the refund depends on the terms of your reservation. You can always contact us if you need help with the process.

data.name: label26.Text
data.value: Yes, you can add additional beds at Stilo Hotel. You can customize your room on our website, where you can also request extra blankets, pillows, bathrobes, and bath towels. Please note that there is an additional fee for these services, and the prices may vary.
